snippet.title: MEATSHOT Announcement Trailer 4K (New Max Payne/The Matrix Inspired Game 2025)
snippet.description:
MEATSHOT Trailer 4K (New Max Payne/The Matrix Inspired Game 2025)

MEATSHOT is a gory, action-packed shooter where you embody an unstoppable beast in a digital realm. Run along walls, dodge bullets, and pull off acrobatic gunfights in slow motion with pinpoint accuracy as you unleash carnage, taking down elite soldiers.

Wishlist the game here:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2537650/MEATSHOT

Follow the dev here:
https://x.com/naezith
